text: Theodorus "Theo" Willems (22 February 1891 - 12 April 1960) was an archer from the Netherlands. Willems competed at the 1920 Summer Olympics.Theo Willems == References == Category:1891 births Category:1960 deaths Category:Dutch archers Category:Olympic gold medalists for the Netherlands Category:Sportspeople from North Brabant
